    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >流血激战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shadow Project 是一款设定在冷战时期背景下的第一人称射击游戏，玩家的任务简单直接：阻止苏联的实验。体验身临其境的战斗，探索氛围浓厚的环境，并经历引人入胜的故事。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/afc1954956e92baa0cefc3f8fa97114a.poster.avif?t=1758162390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/afc1954956e92baa0cefc3f8fa97114a.webm?t=1758162390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/afc1954956e92baa0cefc3f8fa97114a.mp4?t=1758162390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >纽伦堡守则已死</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Shadow Project 中，玩家扮演一名背负悲剧过往的特工，游戏讲述的个人故事将连接过去和现在。美国政府派你的小队深入苏联腹地，调查不道德人体实验的传闻，然而成为实验对象的不仅仅是人类，你将会遭遇远超想象的恐怖。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/ec277421d702f7494a045de82235fc4d.poster.avif?t=1758162390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/ec277421d702f7494a045de82235fc4d.webm?t=1758162390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143530/extras/ec277421d702f7494a045de82235fc4d.mp4?t=1758162390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身临其境的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在精心打造的环境中体验真实而紧张刺激的战斗，玩家可以选择多种不同的战斗方式，无论是正面交火、隐蔽行动，还是寻找秘密捷径，一切都由玩家决定。</p>",
